.row
  .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
    .panel.panel-default.mailing-list
      .panel-body.text-center
        %h2 Want to level up your Javascript-fu?
        %p I write short, focused tutorials on Javascript topics.  Never miss a new article!

        %form(action="//app.mailerlite.com/webforms/submit/g5t8r8" method="POST" target="_blank")
          %input(type="hidden" name="ml-submit" value="1")
          .form-group
            .row.mail-input
              .column.col-md-8.col-xs-12
                %input.form-control.input-lg.col-sm-8(type="email" placeholder="Email address" required name="fields[email]")
              .column.col-md-4.col-xs-12
                %button.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.btn-block Sign up

        %p You'll also be the first to know about some awesome courses I have coming up!
